      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/_Q1NDP8odrXsFYs23mCX8x7zIwhRJJDBfswlv5Xdg2oi86fnFFz8gYSiR_cXYipaK-1J0ULv-ubzkDNhZ7QLzj-cyC3RCFJ3IEw8ieaoqPuGAVbSfnTqz3_iU8UVw-Wp2TgE8Gg4qQ=w2400" title="Time"><blockquote><p>他會吞食一切，蟲魚鳥獸花草樹木，咬破生鐵，蝕穿金鋼，將岩石化成飛灰，殺死國王，屠滅城鎮，滄海化為桑田，高山填成平原。<br>J.R.R. Tolkien - The Hobbits </p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
