      <title>Hello World</title>
      <link href="/Tesatsu/2018/05/04/Hello-World/"/>
      <url>/Tesatsu/2018/05/04/Hello-World/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hello World 對於程式設計師來說, 這是一定要的啦!</p><p>這篇算是這裡的第一篇文章, 用這篇紀念一下.</p><p>之後會慢慢把其他地方的文章轉錄過來, 不過不打算改發表日期所以這篇不會顯示最舊.</p><img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/jFECwc3QjUjZGMhevPdVmng_8Cr5IzBYfy-WHArynC34u4-k3sa01jxXfFlGVwa2xf9fhdJ_MjNAGFfJQxIit4ze_bYQHc08_eNBpEi4mW5tF26Kv-J_5sM7Djlvjm5-WakYXsETow=w2400" title="大觀峰日落"><p>那和這張照片有甚麼關係呢? 其實一點關係都沒有. XD</p><p>照片攝於去年 9 月日本九州大觀峰.</p><p>登頂的時候剛好日落, 很幸運地拍下這張值得紀念的照片.</p><div id="googleMap7245" style="            height: 450px;            width: 100%;            margin: 0px;            padding: 0px            "></div><style>.gmnoprint img {max-width: none !important;}</style><script defer="defer">  window.hexoGmaps = window.hexoGmaps || { maps: {}};  window.hexoGmaps.maps['initgoogleMap7245'] = function init() {    var mapOptions = {       'scrollwheel': false,       'zoom': 13,       'center': new window.google.maps.LatLng( 32.996765 , 131.049611 ),     },     target = document.getElementById('googleMap7245'),     map = new window.google.maps.Map(target, mapOptions);           }  function makeMaps() {    for (var map in window.hexoGmaps.maps) {       console.log('map #', map);       window.hexoGmaps.maps[map]();    }  }  function loadScript() {    window.hexoGmaps.googleScriptLoaded = true;    var script = document.createElement('script');    script.type = 'text/javascript';        script.src = '//maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?v=3.exp&callback=makeMaps&key=AIzaSyCfQ64zXVkp6QwAMFd8BXjJQTp6McM2xMI';    document.body.appendChild(script);  }  if (!window.hexoGmaps.googleScriptLoaded) {    loadScript();  }</script>]]></content>
      
